#MOBILES
#12001
old master~
the Old Master~
The Old Master of the Jujin Kai sits legs crossed, meditating.
~
He is the Old Master of the Jujin Kai.  His eyes have no pupils and are 
large and bulbous.  His skin has a woodish texture and glows a brilliant
gold.  His hair is long and thin, and very sparse.  Beasts from around 
the realm come to him for advice and blessings.  Although he is so old, 
his power is very great which makes you respect him far beyond any other 
creature.  He can see deep into the future and remembers very much about 
the past; he knows much.
~
