#12004
makai demon~
a Makai Demon~
A demon from the Makai world is squealing and screaming here.
~
This demon, like all of his kin is deformed and missahappen.  All three
of his eyes are placed on strange parts of his head, and his arms are 
enlongated and skinny.  He has no mouth that is visible and his legs 
are built like that of a chicken.  He has two fingers on each hand and 
is coated in a viscus clear fluid.  His skin is a deep green and has 
small festering blisters and sores inundating it.  He is wearing some 
sort of strange Makai armor however.
~
