#12005
jujin kai sentry~
a Jujin Kai Sentry~
A Jujin Kai sentry stands fully alerted, waiting for something bad to happen.
~
This young sentry has elongated teeth and what looks like the eyes of 
a cat.  He is one of the Jujin Kai which are a race of half man half 
beasts.  He waits around the his world to kill any intruders. He lurks 
about like an assassin waiting to pounce on a victim that does not 
belong.  He looks very strong, so perhaps it would be a good idea to 
let him be.
~
