jujinkai warrior~
a Jujin Kai Warrior~
A warrior of the Jujin Kai floats here ready to fight.
~
A well trained warrior, this man beast is a formidable apponent.  He 
has the powers and prowess of all of his kind. A strange aura envelopes
his body while he flies, possibly a spell of some kind, or just a side 
effect of his ability to fly.  His teeth are like that of a lion and 
his hair is wild like a mane.  He even has a tail.  He wears simple 
clothes but it does not hide his ability.
~
