arch priest jujin kai~
the Jujin Kai Arch Priest~
An Arch Priest of the Jujin Kai kneels here, meditating.
~
He is an older man, with a completely shaved head and pointed ears.  He 
has red and white paint adorning his face. He has a genuine feeling of 
peace and rest about him.  Looking upon his garments you notice a very 
powerful looking pendant worn around his neck.  Otherwise, all of his 
robes look very common and plain.  He seems not to notice anything but 
his own thoughts.
~
