commoner jujin kai~
a Jujin Kai commoner~
A Jujin Kai commoner walks about, enjoying himself.
~
This man is like all of his brethren. He has long, wild hair, and
feline like teeth.  His ears come to an almost elf-like point, but
are too animalistic.  His eyes are like that of a cat, and he moves with
an inhuman grace.  He has a long tail, and wears clothes of a simple
person.  He is one of the Man-Beast Jujin Kai, and must be treated
with respect.
~
