~
She is a simple commoner of the Jujin Kai realm.  This however does not 
mean she is weak.  Like all of her kind, she has special powers and 
abilities that humans lack.  Her beauty, although primal, is still 
striking.  She has short cropped dark hair that is parted all to one 
side.  She has a shapely body with muscular features usually uncommon 
to human females.
