#ROOMS
#12001
On the Flatland~
You stand on the flats of the Beast World.  In all directions spans the
flatlands, with strange mountains in the distance to the very far north.
To the distant south you can make out a small range of many different 
small mountains.  The sky is a strange pale yellow colour, and the ground
and soil is almost jet black.
